Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真实故事改编
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,1983年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当你爱一个人，你必须相信他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: [Voiceover] When you love someone, you've gotta trust them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别无它法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}There's no other way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你得将掌管生命中一切的那把钥匙给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You've got to give them the key to everything that's yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然有什么意义？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Otherwise, what's the point?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来，我深信我拥有的是这样的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And, for a while, I believed that's the kind of love I had.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在我开赌场及被炸之前…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Before I ever ran a casino, or got blown up...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯罗斯坦，可是最屌的赛马预测者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ace Rothstein was a hell of a handicapper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can tell you that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我旺到每次只要我下注，全国的赌盘赔率…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I was so good that whenever I bet, I'd change the odds...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都会随着改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}for every bookmaker in the country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不盖你，我对赛马的研究精湛到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm serious, I had it down so cold...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让我晋升人间天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}that I was given paradise on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我被升为拉斯维加斯最大赌场之一《坦吉乐》的管理人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I was given one of the biggest casinos in Las Vegas to run, the Tangiers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有聘请我的那帮人才能如此大手笔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}by the only kind of guys that can actually get you that kind of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,六千两百七十万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}$62, 700, 000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道细节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know all the details.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说，没人知道细节…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: [Voiceover] In fact, nobody knew all the details...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原本应该很完美的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but it should've been perfect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他有我这好友尼奇山多罗挺他…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He had me, Nicky Santoro, his best friend, watching his ass...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他手中也揽着他爱的女人，金吉儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and he had Ginger, the woman he loved, on his arm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来，我们全搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But in the end, we fucked it all up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原本应多完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It should've been so sweet, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,结果，我们这样的小混混…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It turned out to be the last time that street guys like us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这次之后就再也无缘搞油水这么丰富的大生意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}were ever given anything that fucking valuable again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那时的赌城，是蠢蛋们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Vegas was a place where suckers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一毛一毛存足了钱飞来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}flew in every year on their own nickel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,直到输光了家当才走人的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and left behind about a billion dollars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在夜晚，你看不到包围拉斯维加斯的沙漠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But at night, you couldn't see the desert that surrounds Las Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但城里许多的问题却都是在沙漠里解决的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But it's in the desert where lots of the town's problems are solved.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠里的坑洞可多着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Got a lot of holes in the desert...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,里面埋藏了很多问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and a lot of problems are buried in those holes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只是程序要对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Except you gotta do it right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你得先把洞挖好…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You gotta have the hole already dug...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,再将货从汽车后车箱载来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}before you show up with a package in the trunk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然你就得在沙漠挖上个30到45分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Otherwise, you're talking about 30 or 45 minutes of digging.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谁又知道期间会有什么人出现？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Who knows who's gonna be coming along in that time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不觉中，你又得多挖好几个洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Before you know it, you gotta dig a few more holes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好一整晚都得耗在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You could be there all fucking night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,坦吉乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,精华地段-拉斯维加斯，十年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}THE STRIP - LAS VEGAS TEN YEARS EARLIER{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谁抗拒的了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Who could resist?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在别处，我只是个登记赛马的一个赌徒…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Anywhere else, I was a bookie, a gambler...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老是得小心翼翼，成天被条子们骚扰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}always looking over my shoulder, hassled by cops, day and night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这儿，我可是罗斯坦先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But here, I'm Mr. Rothstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不但不偷鸡摸狗，还管间赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm not only legitimate, but running a casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就像是将梦想换为现金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And that's like selling people dreams for cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我聘任了赌场的一个老朋友 比利雪伯当经理，然后开始工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I hired an old casino pal, Billy Sherbert, as my manager, and went to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是负责牌室的罗尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And this is Ronnie, who takes care of the card room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,像我们这种人 拉斯维加斯洗去了我们的罪孽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: For guys like me, Las Vegas washes away your sins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,像是道德洗车场一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's like a morality car wash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,它对我们的效用就像法国露德 对驼背和残障的人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It does for us what Lourdes does for humpbacks and cripples.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不但让我们重见天日…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: And along with making us legit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还带来了现金，数不尽的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}comes cash, tons of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你以为我们没事 跑到这沙漠中央干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What do you think we're doing here in the middle of the desert?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了这些钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's all this money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是所有炫目的灯光…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This is the end result of all the bright lights...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的招待、香槟、免费住宿…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and the comped trips, of all the champagne...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,女人与喝不完的酒 最终所造成的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and free hotel suites, and all the broads and all the booze.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是为了 让我们弄走你的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's all been arranged just for us to get your money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是赌城的真面目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's the truth about Las Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是唯一的赢家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}We're the only winners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,赌徒们一点机会都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The players don't stand a chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们的钱从赌桌上…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And their cash flows from the tables...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,流入我们的收银柜再进入保险笼…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}to our boxes through the cage...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,最后流入全赌场最神圣的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and into the most sacred room in the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们计算钱的地方…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The place where they add up all the money...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,注意-请勿进入 万物之首，计算室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the Holy of holies, the count room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿可不是闲杂人等可进出的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now, this place was off-limits.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,连我都进不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Even I couldn't get inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，但我的工作是让它保持 满满的状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But it was my job to keep it filled with cash. That's for sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,里头的钱多到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: They had so much money in there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可让你用百元大钞砌栋房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}you could build a house out of stacks of $100 bills.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒的是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And the best part was that upstairs...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,上头董事会什么屁都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the Board of Directors didn't know what the fuck was going on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们看来一切都干净俐落 没人动手脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}To them everything looked on the up-and-up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗？当然不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Right? Wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,确认五千元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Verify $5,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在计算室的那些人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: The guys in the counting room...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都是被派进去将里头吸干的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}were all slipped in there to skim the joint dry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会少算钱，将计单弄掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They'd do short counts, they'd lose fill slips.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至直接从箱里拿走现款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They'd even take cash right out of the drop-boxes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全是靠这家伙…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And it was up to this guy right here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,站在两百万元前的这位…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}standing in front of $2 million...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在被国税局或任何人发现前…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}to skim the cash off the top without anybody getting wise...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把钱摸走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the IRS or anybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在计算室里 好像都没人在看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Notice how in the count room nobody ever seems to see anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎的，大家都视若无睹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Somehow, somebody's always looking the other way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这些家伙 他们看来真忙，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Look at these guys. They look busy, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在算钱，谁会吵他们呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They're counting money. Who wants to bother them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，天晓得他们会不会 犯了错而忘记偷钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I mean, God forbid they should make a mistake and forget to steal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这期间，你可来去自如\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Meanwhile, you're in and you're out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,走过那些鸟事不干的警卫 每礼拜还多拿一百元…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Past the jag-off guard who gets an extra $100 a week...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只为了看门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}just to watch the door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一如往常一样规律…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's routine. Business as usual...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,走进、走出、你好、再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}in, out, hello, goodbye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's all there is to it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是个拎着皮箱 走出赌场的肥猪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Just another fat fuck walking out of a casino with a suitcase.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但那口箱子 会直接送往一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now, that suitcase was going straight to one place:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,堪萨斯市，那里是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}right to Kansas City, which was as close...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,中部的老大能离拉斯维加斯 最近的地方…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}to Las Vegas as the Midwest bosses could go...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而不用怕被逮捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}without getting themselves arrested.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,堪萨斯市 老大们要的只是那口箱子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That suitcase was all the bosses ever wanted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,每个月都要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And they wanted it every month.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,圣马利诺意大利超市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这个摩门教的混蛋…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now this old Mormon fuck here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他每个月都得拿着箱子飞来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}he had to fly in with suitcases once a month, nice and easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么东西这么香？ -他们做了好料的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Something smells good. -They made us something to eat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老大们会从各地飞来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: The bosses would come from all over:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,底特律、克里夫兰、密尔瓦基…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Detroit, Cleveland, Milwaukee...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,整个中西部…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}all over the Midwest...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都会在这个位于 堪萨斯市的市场碰面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and they would meet in this produce market in Kansas City.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没人会知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nobody even knew it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个让他妈做菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}One of the guys made his mother do the cooking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你有看到杰瑞史塔瑞欧吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Do you ever see that guy Jerry Steriano?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这些老头们看来可能不怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: These old greaseballs might not look it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但相信我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but believe me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才是赌城的秘密操纵者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}these are the guys who secretly controlled Las Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈，那男人又来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}WOMAN: Mama, that man's here again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们控制着 全美卡车司机工会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Because they controlled the Teamsters Union.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而要开赌场非得到那儿去借钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And that's where you had to go to borrow money to buy a casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要放虾吗？ -我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}WOMAN 2: Would you put in shrimp? WOMAN: I would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这些家伙们每月拿不到 这只小箱子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Nobody got a Teamsters' loan unless the guys in this room...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那谁就都别想贷到款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}knew they were gonna get their little suitcases.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,像这从底特律来的老家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Guys like this antique over here, out of Detroit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,或尤其是像利蒙盖吉 这群人的首脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Or especially guys like Remo Gaggi, the outfit's top boss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有大概数字吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You got a round figure on it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是这房里最重要的人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Definitely the most important guy in this room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-十公斤，那就差不多七十万了 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}FRANK: About 20 pounds. Around $700,000. REMO: Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说对拉斯维加斯还有点早…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}STONE: It's a little early for Las Vegas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想邀请赌博游乐业界的 先生与小姐们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but I want to welcome the ladies and gentlemen of the gaming industry....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就以世界所知…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: As far as the world was concerned...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪史东卡车司机工会 退休基金会的负责人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Andy Stone, head of the Teamsters' Pension Fund...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是个清白的人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}was a legitimate guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有权力的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}A powerful man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他与总统一同打高尔夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He played golf with the President.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,代表卡车司机工会退休基金会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ANDY: On behalf of the Teamsters' Pension Fund...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-我很高兴将这… -但安迪也听命于人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm glad to present... SAM: But he also took orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当他被指示将基金贷款 贷给菲立浦葛林…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}When he was told to give a pension-fund loan to Philip Green...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,六千两百七十万的支票…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}...this check for $62,700,000...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给全新的坦吉乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}for the new Tangiers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他就会乖乖听话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}...he did what he was told.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是最完美的傀儡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Here was the perfect front man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他还能干嘛呢？ 他什么都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What the fuck else could he be? He didn't know too much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也什么都不想知道…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He didn't want to know too much...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是老大们让工会借钱给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}especially that the bosses made the Teamsters lend him money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他想相信他们是因为 他的才智贷款给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He wanted to believe they gave him the money because he was smart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解这城市的竞争性有多大 才会说出此话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I say that knowing just how much competition we have in this city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从哪儿找来葛林的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: And where they got Green from?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道啊？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Who the fuck knows?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道他在亚利桑那州 是个房地产经纪…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}All I know is that he was an Arizona real-estate hustler...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,却连开来拿支票的油钱 都差点付不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}who barely had enough gas money to come and pick up his fucking check.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,美国中部 卡车司机工会退休基金 是由老大的人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And it was the bosses' man...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪史东下所有的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Andy Stone, who gave all the orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是由董事会主席 菲立浦葛林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Not the Chairman of the Board, Philip Green.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只缺…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Now all they needed was...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一个可信任的人来管理赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}someone they could trust to run the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁比艾斯更适合？ 他已经在赌城混了几年…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And who better than Ace? He was already in Vegas a couple years...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他对这儿瞭若指掌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and he had the fucking place clocked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯的一贯作风 你给他个管理赌场的机会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But typical Ace, give him a shot to run a casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他还推三阻四\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and he tries to talk you out of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道自己行不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't know if I could do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,赌博游乐委员会绝不会 发执照给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The Gaming Commission would never give me a license.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我最起码有两打以上 赌博与赛马被逮的前科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I have at least 24 gambling and bookmaking pinches on me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在赌场工作不需要执照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You don't have to have a license to work in a casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要去申请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}All you gotta do is apply for one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,州法律允许你在申请期间…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The State law says that you can work in a casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在赌场做事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}while they process your application.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们文件进度现在落后十年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ANDY: They got a 10-year backlog.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,若他们发现了怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What happens when they do find out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么会想发现？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ANDY: Why would they want to find out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这儿投资了一亿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}We're putting $100 million here.{\r}
