Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你是个蠢才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}'Cause you're a jag-off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起？ -什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Excuse me. -What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是你的笔吗？ -是我的，怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Isthis your pen? -Yeah, that's my pen. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很好看，我不知道是谁的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's nice. I didn't know whose it was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想它弄丢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I didn't want it to get lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 你为什么不拿那只笔…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thank you. Why don't you take that fucking pen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,捅到你屁眼里去，你这蠢才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and shove it up your ass, you fucking jag-off?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只是… -王八蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Well, I was just offering-- -Asshole.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小心，乔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}MAN: Look out, Joe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？ 你有没有听到女孩哭？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What's that? You hear a little girl?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是个小女孩吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Is that a little fucking girl?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,刚叫我朋友捅什么的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What happened to the tough guy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个硬汉呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}who told my friend to stick it up his fucking ass?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇，够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky, take it easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在想那人 为什么这么说时…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: While I tried to figure out why the guy said what he said...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇就动手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky just hit him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不管一个人多大个子 尼奇都会跟他拼命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}No matter how big a guy might be, Nicky would take him on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿拳头打他 他就会拿球棒回你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You beat Nicky with fists, he comes back with a bat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿刀捅他 他就会用枪射你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You beat him with a knife, he comes back with a gun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你若拿枪射他 那你最好是杀了他…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If you beat him with a gun, you'd better kill him...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他会一直不停的回来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}because he'll keep coming back and back...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你挂了为止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}until one of you is dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,由我保护艾斯…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: With me protecting Ace...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他为老大们狠狠赚了一票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}he made a fortune for the bosses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他来赌城的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's what got him to Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他根本就是印钞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He was a money machine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为这些家伙赚大钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}A tremendous earner for these guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他一来就把供金增加了一倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}As soon as he took over, he doubled the fucking drop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯来后，赌场从就没见过 那么多的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}With Ace, the casino never saw so much money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老大们当然是笑不拢嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And the bosses, they couldn't be happier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在赌城，我还得跟附近有关系的 一些牛仔找事做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: In Vegas, I had to keep a few juiced-in local cowboys working.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们与老家伙们很熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They were close to the good old boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是我们 那些家伙现在都还在铲驴粪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Without us, these guys would still be shoveling mule shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,场子得保持干净\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You've got to keep a cleaner station.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,需要清洁工就呼叫他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If you need Mr. Clean, page him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下次不会了，山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Won't happen again, Sam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-罗斯坦先生 -下次不会了，罗斯坦先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Mr. Rothstein. MAN: It won't happen again, Mr. Rothstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙又是一个蠢白人吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Is this guy just another dumb fucking white man, or what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-你需要他 -弄不走是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You need this guy. -Can't get rid of him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他有关系的 他是县辅导的表兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's juiced in. He's the County Commissioner's cousin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我连清洁工都不会给他做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: I wouldn't give the bum a mop job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别无选择，我必须照顾他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I had no choice. I had to take care of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这些乡巴佬当权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}These yokels ran the state.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢，议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}DEALER: Thanks, Senator.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们立法，又掌管法院 -我要开房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: They passed the laws, owned the courts. I need a room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我每周都有十多个政客来访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: I had dozens of politicians and state officials coming through weekly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-他要什么都给他 -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Get him what he wants. BILLY: Certainly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,何不让他们快乐？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Why not make them happy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对于政客 例如我们这位州议员…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}For politicians, like our State Senator up there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是免费的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}everything was on the house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的招待生涯 在当选时就赢得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}These guys won their comped life when they got elected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,何不加以利用？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Why not take advantage of it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,政客还是小事，我们解决的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Still, the politicians came cheap. We could handle them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是像市川那种…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's a whale, like K.K. Ichikawa...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,百家乐一把下三万的豪赌客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}who plays $30, 000 a hand in baccarat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这种才该看紧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's the one you really gotta watch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他下注动作快，玩得大 他的资金雄厚…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He plays fast and big. He has the cash and the credit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,足可把你玩垮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}to turn out your lights.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一年前他让开曼群岛上 好几家赌场洗底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}A year ago he cleaned out a couple of casinos in the Cayman Islands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他从赌场赢了我们两百万…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Downstairs he takes us for $2 million...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又从酒店套房拿了免费的 肥皂、洗发精与毛巾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and upstairs he takes free soap, shampoo and towels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一个 喜爱免费套房…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Another billionaire cheapskate who loved his free rooms...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,免费私人飞机又赚得我们两百万 的亿万富翁小气鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}free private jets and $2 million of our money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不好惹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But we got him back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我让机师告诉他飞机故障\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I had our pilot tell him the plane was on the fritz.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-发生什么事？ -非常抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ICHlKAWA: What went wrong? BILLY: I'm awfully sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是机械故障\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}These mechanical things happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿总比在上面好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Better here than up there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他赶不上回日本的飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Then he missed the flights connecting with Japan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然没有空房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can't believe there's no room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给了他一整楼的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: We got him back with a whole floor of rooms to himself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-真抱歉让你赶不上飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Sorry you missed your plane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想要赢回我的钱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You'd like some of my money back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不赌了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, no. No gambling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他回来后开始下小注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: And once he was back, he played small.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一把只赌一千 而不是平常的三万一把\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He bet $1,000 a hand, instead of his usual $30,000 a hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道这些豪赌客的习性…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But I knew the trick with whales like Ichikawa...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不可能一直下小注的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}was that they can't bet small for long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他不觉得是赢一万…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He didn't think of it as winning $10, 000...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他会想成是输九万…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}he thought of it as losing $90, 000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他开始加码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, he upped his bets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,直到他将赢得的输光 再加上自己一百万的现金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Until he dropped his winnings back and gave up $1 million of his own cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在赌场里，第一原则就是 让他们一直赌…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}In a casino, the cardinal rule is to keep them playing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也让他们一直回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and keep them coming back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,赌得越多就输得越多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The longer they play, the more they lose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最终钱就都是我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}In the end, we get it all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在赌城，每个人都得注意着别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}In Vegas, everybody's gotta watch everybody else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,玩家是来赢赌场钱的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Since the players are looking to beat the casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,庄家得看好玩家…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the dealers are watching the players...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,收付赌注得看好庄家…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the boxmen are watching the dealers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,管场的注意着收付赌注的人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the floormen are watching the boxmen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,赌区经理看着管场的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the pit bosses are watching the floormen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,值班经理看着赌区经理…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the shift bosses are watching the pit bosses...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,赌场经理看着值班经理…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the casino manager is watching the shift bosses...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我则看着赌场经理…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm watching the casino manager...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而监视照相机看着我们大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and the eye in the sky is watching us all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,另外，还有十多个家伙…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Plus, we had a dozen guys...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大多以前都是老千 他们知道所有的骗术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}most of them ex-cheats, who knew every trick in the house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常好 -我就跟你说我今天很旺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Very nice. -I told you I was hot tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Looking good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，为了金吉儿，快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}MAN: Let's go. This is for Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一百赌你没老A\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}MAN: Let me have $100 on your hard 10.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}MAN: Here we go now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起 -骰子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Oh, I'm sorry. -The dice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:22:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thank you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I appreciate that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,保重，史蒂夫 要冒险啊，开快车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Take care, Steve. Take chances, drive fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这一百给你，甜心 多谢你赏光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This $100 is for you, love. Thanks for your time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-快点 -怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Come on. -What's the matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你赚了不少，我要我的份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I made a lot of money for you, I want my cut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什么钱？我看到你偷钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What money? I've seen you stealing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,“什么钱？” 你看看这堆筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}"What money?" Look at the stack of chips.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要我的一半 -我观察你一夜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: I want my half. GAMBLER: I've watched you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要我的钱 -你皮包里全是熟筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-I want my money. -Your bag is full of chips.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-我才没偷你的东西 -滚吧！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: I didn't steal anything from you. GAMBLER: Get lost!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-滚吧？ -没错！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Get lost? GAMBLER: Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-这怎么样呢？ -别这样！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Well, how about that? -Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.21,0:24:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真酷，让我一见钟情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: What a move. I fell in love right there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.47,0:24:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但在赌城，像金吉儿这样的女孩 得花上大钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But in Vegas, for a girl like Ginger, love costs money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我去补个妆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm gonna go powder my nose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-金吉儿的人生目标是钱 -马上回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Ginger's mission in life was money. I'll be right back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-待会见，金吉儿 -多谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}DOORMAN: See you. GINGER: Thanks for asking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.17,0:24:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她在赌场可是皇后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: She was a queen around the casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.00,0:25:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她召来大赌客 并也帮他们花大钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}She brought in high rollers and helped them spend a lot of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.80,0:25:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好 -嘿，金吉儿，你好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Hello. -Hey, Ginger. How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.09,0:25:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好得很，一点小意思 你帮我搞定了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Great. You might have something for me. Got me covered?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.85,0:25:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常感谢 -自己保重喔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Thank you. VALET: Take care of yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些幸运丸给你，安迪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I got some lucky pills for you, Andy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.94,0:25:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谁不想要金吉儿？ 她是城里名声最响亮…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Who didn't want her? She was one of the best known...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.77,0:25:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也是道上最受欢迎的江湖人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}best liked and most respected hustlers in town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.78,0:25:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,像她这么聪明的玩家 可以让男人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Smart hustlers like her could keep a guy awake...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.24,0:25:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,两三天不睡 然后再让他一文不名的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}for two or three days before sending him home broke...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.79,0:25:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,回到老婆与银行审查主任身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}to the little woman and his bank examiners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.22,0:25:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有找钱吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Any change?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.77,0:25:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来时小赌了几把\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, I hit a few games on the way back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.61,0:25:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那根本是胡扯 她把钱收起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: But that was all bullshit. She just pocketed the cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.57,0:25:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-你今天好吗？ -不错啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: How you doing tonight? CASHlER: Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.57,0:26:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你呢？ -衰死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}CASHlER: How are you? GINGER: Beat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.24,0:26:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-金吉儿洞悉玩家们的习性 -给你一百\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Ginger had the hustlers' code. GINGER: Take one for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.96,0:26:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-多谢 -她懂得如何买通他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}CASHlER: Thank you. SAM: She knew how to take care of people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是赌城的座右铭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's what Vegas is all about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.17,0:26:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-六千八百元 -谢啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}CASHlER: $6,800. GINGER: Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-这里是讲究回扣的城市 -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: It's kickback city. GINGER: Have a good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.18,0:26:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她罩庄家…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: She took care of the dealers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.27,0:26:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,赌区经理，管场经理…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}pit bosses, floor managers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.90,0:26:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但尤其关照停车小弟…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but, mostly, the valet parkers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.44,0:26:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能帮你找到任何东西 也能帮你解决任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the guys who could get you anything and take care of anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.86,0:26:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉儿搞定了停车的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ginger took care of the parkers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.70,0:26:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们搞定警卫 而警卫会摆平警察…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}who took care of the security guards, who took care of the cops...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.28,0:26:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-让她可继续开工 -我今晚需要那东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}who let her operate. I need that stuff tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.00,0:26:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-没问题 -你真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}VALET: No problem. GINGER: You are a doll.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.62,0:26:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,停车赚的钱多到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: The valet parking job was such a money-maker...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.96,0:26:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,得买通酒店经理才能排上空缺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}they had to pay off the hotel manager just to get the concession.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.17,0:26:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有一点我不懂…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But one thing I didn't understand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.51,0:26:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她将一切都控制的好好的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}was that she had everything under control...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.14,0:26:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,却被她那拉皮条的男友 莱丝特戴蒙德吃得死死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}except for her old pimp boyfriend, Lester Diamond.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.98,0:27:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我得顾到其他人，我的搭挡们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I got other people in this. I got partners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.52,0:27:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在这事上有我罩你，知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm looking out for you in this thing, okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.48,0:27:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你将获你应得的 而且第一个拿到，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You'll get yours back, and you'll get it back first. Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.32,0:27:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的 -你去哪儿了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-All right. -Where you going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.83,0:27:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿？ 你又飘走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Where are you? You're in that place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.66,0:27:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-我在这儿 -不，你不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-I'm here. -No, you're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.71,0:27:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Where are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.83,0:27:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远在你身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm always here for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.92,0:27:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You are. -I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.01,0:27:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我所认识的金吉儿 根本不会多看这怪胎一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: The Ginger I knew wouldn't even look at this creep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.01,0:27:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝你好运 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Good luck. -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.01,0:27:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个老千，专作假牌…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: He was a moocher, a card cheat...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.85,0:27:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老在高尔夫俱乐部招摇撞骗 一个瘪三…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}a country club golf hustler, a scumbag...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.98,0:27:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-为了几块钱追着牙医屁股跑 -小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-chasing dentists for a few bucks. -Careful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.69,0:27:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他永远都没钱，永远都有藉口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: He was always broke. He always had a story.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.15,0:27:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何，她却拒绝不了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Somehow, she could never turn him down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.53,0:27:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在金吉儿眼里，他只是运气不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The way Ginger saw it was that he was just an unlucky guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.03,0:27:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人照顾他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Somebody had to take care of him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.49,0:27:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在老家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}BACK HOME{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.62,0:27:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但尼奇可不需要人照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But nobody had to take care of Nicky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.54,0:27:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到现金的话 我们就跟你平分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You find any cash in there, we'll whack it up with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.29,0:27:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他把自己照顾得太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: He took care of himself only too well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.84,0:28:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是为什么老家的条子 都想抓他到案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's why every badge back home wanted to nail him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.51,0:28:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我将这些都折得好好的 能不能放尊重点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I folded these things beautifully. I would appreciate a little respect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.39,0:28:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别看我，兄弟 我还得跟她同床共枕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't look at me, pal, I gotta live with her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.72,0:28:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就连去渡个假 他们在机场时都不放过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Even after a vacation, they hassled him at the airport.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.56,0:28:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰克玛雷诺在那儿等他 条子们也在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Frank Marino was there to meet him. So were the cops.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.40,0:28:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想逮他…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They wanted to pinch him...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.19,0:28:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-因为一宗在安特卫普的钻石窃案 -帮忙折吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-for a diamond burglary in Antwerp. -Help me fold these.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.82,0:28:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们随时愿意嫁祸于他 不管是在哪儿发生什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: They were ready to blame him for anything, no matter where.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.32,0:28:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们通常是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They were usually right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.74,0:28:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,因为尼奇很喜欢混帮派\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Because Nicky enjoyed being a gangster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.70,0:28:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他也不在乎有谁知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And he didn't give a damn who knew it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.12,0:28:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看看，美极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: There we go. Look at that. Beautiful!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.75,0:28:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,让我担心的是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: I mean that's what worried me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.25,0:28:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇似乎要被派来拉斯维加斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}'cause it turns out, Nicky was about to be sent to Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.42,0:28:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-好了，就这样 -还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}JENNlFER: All right, we're clear. NICKY: There's more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.26,0:28:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一定还有些卡在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: There's a couple stuck in there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.26,0:28:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-我告诉你都拿出来了 -快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-I'm telling you, they're out! -Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.22,0:28:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别急于辩护 可能还有些卡在你头发里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't get so defensive, it could be stuck in your hair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.27,0:28:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.61,0:28:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了，谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}There's no more. Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.78,0:28:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我迫不及待想去拉斯维加斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I couldn't wait to get my hands on Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.82,0:29:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但老大可不是送我去玩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But the bosses didn't send me out to have a good time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.62,0:29:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要我去确保 没人找艾斯的麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They sent me out to make sure that nobody fucked with Ace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也确保没人干扰每月的抽头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And nobody interfered with the fucking skim.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.67,0:29:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-嘿 -你好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Hey. -Hey, how you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.13,0:29:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hey, Sammy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.80,0:29:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-天呀，瞧瞧这地方 -不可思议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Boy, look at this place. -Incredible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.30,0:29:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来赌城\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Welcome to Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.85,0:29:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-好样的，山姆 -不错吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Okay, Sammy. SAM: Something, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.81,0:29:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.65,0:29:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,靠，你都在这儿干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Holy shit. What've you been doing out here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,甜心，过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Honey, come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.99,0:29:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是珍妮佛与尼克 我的好朋友们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This is Jennifer and Nick. They're dear friends of mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.58,0:29:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好，珍妮佛 -幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Hi, Jennifer. -A pleasure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.66,0:29:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的，山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Okay, Sammy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.50,0:29:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐后，我们让珍妮佛 与金吉儿一块儿…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: After we ate, we left Jennifer and Ginger...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.21,0:29:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩则出去谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and we took a ride to talk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.13,0:29:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他对我丢了颗炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And then, he hit me with it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.59,0:29:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我也搬来如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What do you think about me moving out here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.51,0:29:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You got a problem with that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.22,0:29:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, of course not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.56,0:30:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说你允许罗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You mean I have your permission?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.52,0:30:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当然罗 但我得告诉你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sure, you do. But I just gotta tell you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.69,0:30:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿可不能开玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}it's no joke out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.73,0:30:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你得保持低调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You gotta keep a low profile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不像是在老家 这儿他们不喜欢我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's not like back home. They don't like guys like us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.91,0:30:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,警长是个不折不扣的牛仔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This sheriff's a real cowboy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,连巡警都不怕在沙漠里埋人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Even coppers aren't afraid to bury people in the desert.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎 我只想离开老家一阵子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't care. I want to get away from back home for a while.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.92,0:30:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我厌倦了那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm tired of that shit back there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.92,0:30:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这地方，简直是钱砌的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Look at this place. It's made of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.84,0:30:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,知道最屌的是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know what the best part is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.38,0:30:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道我们在干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nobody's gonna know what we're doing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.38,0:30:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没人看着我们，大家都在老家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}There's nobody here to see us. Everybody's back home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.55,0:30:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我无缘故被逮了两次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I got pinched twice for no reason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.47,0:30:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我真得小心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I really gotta be careful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.27,0:30:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我管理的地方是有执照的 全是合法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm running a licensed place. Everything's legit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.89,0:30:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心，我什么都不会做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't worry about it. I'm not gonna do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.60,0:30:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我尤其不会拖你下水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm especially not gonna involve you in anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.78,0:30:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯看赌城的观点…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Ace saw Vegas one way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.57,0:30:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-你跟他说过我要来吗？ -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Call and tell him I'm coming? JACK: Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.91,0:30:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的看法不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}...but I saw it another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.58,0:30:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我视它为未开发的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I saw it as untouched.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.25,0:30:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,多的是可勒索的赌马组头 皮条客与毒贩…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They had bookies, pimps, and drug dealers I could shake down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.25,0:31:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能找谁靠？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Who the fuck were they gonna run to?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.26,0:31:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始一个一个下手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}So I started getting everybody in line.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.22,0:31:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,最屌的是，我这辈子第一次…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Best of all, for the first time in my life...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.97,0:31:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,发觉了稳赢的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I figured out a way not to lose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.47,0:31:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他是有个稳赢之计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: He had a foolproof scheme.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.43,0:31:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不高明，但起码行得通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It wasn't very scientific, but it worked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.64,0:31:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他赢时就收钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}When he won, he collected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.06,0:31:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,输时就叫赌马组头去死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}When he lost, he told the bookies to fuck off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.65,0:31:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能怎样？逼迫尼奇？ 尼奇就是逼迫者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What were they gonna do? Muscle Nicky? Nicky was the muscle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.95,0:31:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好吗？ -你好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Hey, how you doing? -How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.78,0:31:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有东西给我吗？ -什么东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You got that thing for me? -What thing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.95,0:31:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇，我以为你是来下注的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky, I thought you was laying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.12,0:31:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,下注？不，我来收钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I was laying? No, I'm taking it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.96,0:31:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-你确定？ -非常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You sure? -I'm positive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.96,0:31:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-我搞混了 -你搞混了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-I'm a little confused. -You're a little confused?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.17,0:31:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,或许在我把你的脸砸过这窗户后…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Maybe if I stick your fucking face through this window...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.01,0:31:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会清楚点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}you'll get unconfused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.68,0:31:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-把钱他妈的给我 -对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Give me the fucking money. -I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.60,0:31:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I didn't mean anything by it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.01,0:31:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你连钱都准备好了 你他妈的以为我要下注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's why you had it ready. You thought I was laying it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.81,0:31:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的头 -放聪明点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-My fucking head. -Smarten up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.48,0:31:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在尼可拉斯山多罗 要来跟我们说第一总统的故事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And now Nicholas Santoro will come up and tell us about our first President.{\r}
