Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.71,0:38:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-还玩得愉快吗？ -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}BILLY: Having a good time? HUSTLER 2: Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.55,0:38:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在较有隐私的地方算比较好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You want to count the money in privacy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.89,0:38:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我得赶飞机去克里夫兰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}HUSTLER 2: I have a plane to catch.{\r}
