Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.74,0:38:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你那群朋友，他们若来乱搞 会发生什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Tell your friends what happens if they fuck around here.{\r}
