Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.92,0:38:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要是再敢回来 我会敲烂你们的头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: If you come back, either one of you, we'll break your fucking heads.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.59,0:38:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那锯子没？不是放着好看的 不要再出现在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You see that fucking saw? We're gonna use it. You don't fuck around here.{\r}
