Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.43,0:38:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-给我滚 -谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Get out of here. -Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.30,0:38:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把他丢到后街去 跟条子说他被车撞到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Throw him out in the alley. Tell the cops he got hit by a car.{\r}
