Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.99,0:39:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不年轻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}We're not getting any younger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.86,0:39:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得是时候了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't you think it's time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.86,0:39:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你对这些不厌烦吗？ 这边睡、那边混？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Aren't you getting tired of all this shit? Banging around, hustling around?{\r}
