Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.75,0:39:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想娶你进门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm trying to marry you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.71,0:39:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你想嫁我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: You wanna marry me?{\r}
