Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.85,0:39:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我会是个好爸爸 你也将是个好妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'd be a good father, you'd be a good mother.{\r}
