Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.49,0:39:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我心目中最理想的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can't think of anybody better to be with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.33,0:39:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't feel like waiting anymore.{\r}
