Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.84,0:40:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很现实，我可以接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm realistic. I can accept that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.76,0:40:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爱到底是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: What is love anyway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.55,0:40:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是互相尊重 不就是一心一意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: It's a mutual respect. It's a devotion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.31,0:40:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个人在乎另一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's a caring from one person to another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.10,0:40:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,若我们可以设立一个基础…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And if we could set up some kind of foundation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.15,0:40:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,以相互尊重为底…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}based on that mutual respect...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.28,0:41:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得迟早你会对我有情…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I feel that eventually you would care enough about me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.41,0:41:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我能接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}that I could live with that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.45,0:41:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,若行不通的话…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If it doesn't work out...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.33,0:41:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,若行不通的话 那我怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}if it doesn't play out, then what happens to me?{\r}
