Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.67,0:41:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我们俩行不通…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}if it doesn't work out between us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.67,0:41:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我都会确保你下半辈子的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll make sure you're okay for the rest of your life.{\r}
