Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.06,0:41:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你下半辈子都不用愁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You'll be set up for the rest of your life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.98,0:41:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这我可保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That I can promise you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.07,0:41:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要试试？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Want to take a chance?{\r}
