Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.46,0:41:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不在乎 我是山姆罗斯坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but I didn't give a fuck. I'm Sam Rothstein, I said.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.26,0:41:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我能改变她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can change her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.97,0:42:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是典型的艾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: It was typical Ace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他请了城里所有的大人物 他知道他们都会出席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He invited the biggest people in town. He knew they'd show.{\r}
