Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.19,0:42:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在心里？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}In your heart?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.23,0:42:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别等我过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't make me come there.{\r}
