Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.29,0:47:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我得要信任你到可将生命交给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I have to be able to trust you with my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.17,0:47:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,洛杉矶
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.30,0:47:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,总价值超过一百万的现金与珠宝 锁在赌城的银行里…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: With over $1 million in cash and jewels tucked in a bank in Vegas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.10,0:47:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,全归她所有 金吉儿非常有安全感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}only for Ginger, she was secure and happy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.43,0:47:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她最爱那些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}She loved that shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.31,0:47:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但在我这行里 手上得有许多流动的现金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But a guy in my line of work has to have a lot of payoff cash around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.57,0:47:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,贪污的条子与绑匪 他们都不收支票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Crooked cops and kidnappers, they don't take checks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.73,0:47:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,考林先生，需要帮忙吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Need any help with that, Mr. Collins?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.86,0:47:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在洛杉矶的银行里 也摆了两百万…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: So I put $2 million cash in a Los Angeles bank...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.49,0:47:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用考林先生与夫人的名义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}under the name of Mr. and Mrs. Tom Collins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.74,0:47:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这纯粹是我个人的赎金与保金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This was strictly my shakedown and kidnapping money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.12,0:47:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在我最需要这笔钱时 我不是蹲在牢里就是被关在衣柜…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Since I'd be in jail or locked in a closet when I needed the money most...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.67,0:47:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我将这笔钱唯一的钥匙 给了金吉儿好让我能保命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I gave Ginger the only key to the cash that could get me back alive.{\r}
