Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.94,0:48:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一可以开保险箱的人 连我都开启不了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}to have total access to the box, no one else, including myself?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.49,0:48:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，这是你的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}BANKER: That's right. That's the way you wanted it.{\r}
