Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.54,0:48:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，怎么啦？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sure I do. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.13,0:48:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊，只是很少见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's good. It's just unusual.{\r}
