Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.90,0:49:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为了安全起见，我又将头衔…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}To play it safe, I switched job titles again...{\r}
