Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.82,0:49:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来就没人可以 为执照的事找我麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This way nobody would bother me about a license.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.49,0:49:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,赌城对我来说像是个梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Vegas was like a dream for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.58,0:49:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是尼奇也梦想着 他自己的赌城\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Trouble was Nicky was dreaming of his own kind of Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.50,0:49:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我将钱放出，每天三分利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I put money out on the street charging three points a week.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.87,0:49:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,庄家高利贷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Juice to the dealers.{\r}
