Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.64,0:53:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，她会被解雇 送她回巴黎…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's right, she will get fired. Send her back to Paris--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.48,0:53:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们一贯的做法是… -停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-It's been our policy-- -Stop everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.73,0:53:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-她很出名 -这就是问题，她太懒散\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}AGENT: She's an institution. SAM: That's the problem. She's lazy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.02,0:54:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我得佩服这家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I gotta give the guy credit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.98,0:54:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 他做了最明显的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I mean, he does the most obvious thing.{\r}
