Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.70,0:54:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不加以利用呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}So why not take advantage, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.91,0:54:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他把签注从街上…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}So he took bookie joints off the street...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.45,0:54:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,开到赌场内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and opened them up inside the casino.{\r}
