Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.09,0:54:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的创意…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Between my innovations...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.30,0:54:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,加上尼奇对工作的投入…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and Nicky's dedication to his job...{\r}
