Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.56,0:54:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点，你最近很引人注目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Watch yourself. There's a lot of heat on you.{\r}
