Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.90,0:54:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我从警卫那儿听来的 他们以前都曾是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm hearing things from security. They're all ex-cops.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.53,0:54:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,警长已将你放入黑名单了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The sheriff wants to put you in the Black Book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.28,0:54:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那黑名单根本就是个屁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That Black Book is a bunch of bullshit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.41,0:54:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,全国只有两个人的名字在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}There's two names in it for the whole country...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.62,0:54:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,教父艾尔卡邦就是其中之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and one of them is still Al Capone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.49,0:54:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你上了名单麻烦就大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They put you in that book, you're gonna be in trouble.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.37,0:54:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你将进不了赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You won't be able to walk into a casino.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.42,0:55:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只不过是在养家活口罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm trying to make a living, that's all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.83,0:55:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是跟你讲一声 别说我没警告你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm just telling you. Don't say I didn't warn you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.22,0:55:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯坦夫人，请看前面 很好，谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}PHOTOGRAPHER: Mrs. Rothstein, straight ahead. Very nice. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.35,0:55:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因他的努力与认真…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}PHILIP: For his hard work and dedication...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.69,0:55:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,与他为拉斯维加斯带来的新生命…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and the new life blood he has instilled in Las Vegas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.94,0:55:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆将自己建立为赌博游乐业界…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sam has established himself as an indispensable member...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.98,0:55:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不可缺乏的成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}of the gaming community.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.45,0:55:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,以坦吉乐赌博游乐集团 董事长的名义…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}As the head of the Tangiers Gaming Corporation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.86,0:55:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我很容幸为你们介绍 山姆罗斯坦…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}it's my pleasure to welcome Sam Rothstein...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.37,0:55:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,维加斯谷乡村俱乐部新成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}to the Vegas Valley Country Club.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.83,0:55:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉许状
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.50,0:55:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在老家，我所做的 早就让我蹲牢房去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Back home, they'd put me in jail for what I'm doing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.25,0:55:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这儿，他们却颁奖给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But out here, they're giving me awards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.63,0:55:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我很荣幸能获得…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It is with great pleasure that I accept this certificate of appreciation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.09,0:55:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯维加斯慈善基金会 颁发的嘉许奖状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}from the Charitable Foundations of Greater Las Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.97,0:55:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你，甜心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Congratulations, sweetheart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.68,0:56:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆募得了有史来 最多的捐款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sam raised more than we've ever raised before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.73,0:56:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但我最爱的还是看着我老婆 金吉儿周旋全场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: But my greatest pleasure was watching my wife work the room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.61,0:56:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们爱死她了 但你又怎能不爱她？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They all loved her. How could you not love her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.49,0:56:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她是世上最有魅力的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}She could be the most charming woman you ever saw.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.95,0:56:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,人们都喜欢在她身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}People loved to be around her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.87,0:56:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定得带艾美来参加 莎夏的生日派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You've got to bring Amy to Sasha's birthday party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.34,0:56:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,星期六下午三点 我们很希望她能来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}LADY: We'd love to have her there. 3:00, Saturday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.92,0:56:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的 -太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Yes, okay. -Great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.93,0:56:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她让大家都开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: She made everybody feel good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.81,0:56:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-恭喜你，山姆 -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Congratulations, Sam. -Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.44,0:56:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，罗斯坦夫人，你好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Hello, Mrs. Rothstein. How are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.20,0:56:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我见过最美丽的女人 罗斯坦先生，你真是个幸运的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're one of the most gorgeous women I've seen. You're a lucky man, Mr. Rothstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.62,0:56:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thanks for that compliment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.54,0:56:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他是赌场里的小伙子 挺好又聪明的小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: He was a young kid from the casino. Nice kid. Bright boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.55,0:56:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这小子真他妈的带种 我第二天就炒了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What balls on this fucking kid. The next day I fired him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.05,0:57:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉儿对人就是有这种魅力 她甚至鼓励他们这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ginger had that effect on people. I think she even encouraged them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.81,0:57:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看看这件吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Do you wanna see this one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.77,0:57:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸帮我买了这么多珠宝 因为他好爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Daddy gave me all this jewelry because he loves me so much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.03,0:57:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但不管他们多爱她…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: But as much as they loved her...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.74,0:57:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Fabulous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.95,0:57:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都不知道什么让她感动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}...they didn't know what really moved her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.91,0:57:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Look at this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.70,0:57:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸给我的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Daddy gave me....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.12,0:57:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉儿快快乐乐的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: With Ginger happy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.81,0:57:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我才能专心去做我所专长的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I was able to concentrate on what I knew best.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.67,0:57:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,较松的机器都在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Loose machines are right back over there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.25,0:57:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在那儿干嘛？ 看都看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What are they doing back there? You can't even see them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.80,0:57:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.84,0:57:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那最大累积奖金的那些呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What about the progressives with the high jackpots?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.14,0:57:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是我们最好的机子 都是靠它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}These are our best machines. They bring all the action.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.73,0:57:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪盈收变少了 重头戏都在前面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}No wonder the drop is off. The action is in the front.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.81,0:57:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-摆到前面去 -好的，我会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Bring them up front. -All right, I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.98,0:57:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 在这有三种做事方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Listen carefully. There are three ways of doing things here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.24,0:57:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的、不正确的 和我的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The right way, the wrong way, and the way that I do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.91,0:57:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-懂了没？ -我懂了，马上去办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Understand? -I do understand. I'll get right on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.87,0:57:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢 -别谢我，去做就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Thank you. -Don't thank me. Just do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.83,0:57:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你是吃角子老虎机的经理 我不应该还需要告诉你这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're the slots manager. I shouldn't have to tell you this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.42,0:58:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,唉，你说得真对 真是抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Dang, you are right. I'm so sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.09,0:58:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我一天得工作18个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: So I ended up working 18-hour days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.72,0:58:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉儿反倒是成为 真正享受赌城的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ginger was the one who wound up enjoying the best of Vegas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.06,0:58:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟我来，我带您去更好的桌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Come with me, please. I have a better table for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.98,0:58:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底跟那王八蛋说了些什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What did you say to that fucking jerk, anyway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.61,0:58:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟她说我是罗斯坦夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I told him that I was Mrs. Sam Rothstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.57,0:58:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当然得加以利用罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You might as well get something out of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.87,0:58:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不久后我所担心的事就发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: It wasn't long before what I was afraid was gonna happen, happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.83,0:58:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇把自己搞到成为 全赌城的拒绝往来户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky managed to get himself banned from every casino in Vegas.{\r}
