Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.86,1:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须要了解 而我也相信你了解…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You have to understand, and I'm sure you do...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.03,1:03:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,做这种风险大的投资…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}that in a venture of this kind...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.82,1:03:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要有可能亏损的心理准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}you must be prepared to take some kind of loss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.70,1:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我将一些钱交给查理克拉克 艾斯的银行经理，做一些正当投资\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I put some money in legitimate deals with Charlie Clark, Ace's banker.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.58,1:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你会尽力而为，不是吗？ -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You will try to push it through, won't you? -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.21,1:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你得了解我现在 给了你五万元现金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You got to understand, I'm giving you $50,000 cash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.54,1:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我将更多钱投入正当的投资 例如我开的餐馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Then I put more money in some legitimate places, like my restaurant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.34,1:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-剩这个了？ -是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}DOMINICK: Is that the last one? COOK: Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.93,1:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我让我小弟，多明尼可经营\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I had my kid brother, Dominick, run it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.56,1:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,王八蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Fuckers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.77,1:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}DOMINICK: Here you go, guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.27,1:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢了 -慢慢享用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Thanks a lot. -Enjoy it. Have a good time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.94,1:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-噎死你，王八蛋 -嗨，小多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Choke on it, motherfucker. -Hi, Dom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.82,1:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.20,1:04:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，尼奇很喜欢餐馆 他对开餐厅也很拿手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Yeah, Nicky loved restaurants. He was a real restaurant buff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.20,1:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年来，他逢开餐厅必赚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And over the years, he always made money with them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.92,1:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他在拉斯维加斯开了比萨斜塔 很受大家欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}In Vegas, he had the Leaning Tower. It was a very popular spot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.42,1:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,常有政客、脱衣舞娘 还有电影明星光顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He had politicians, showgirls and movie stars hanging out all over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.93,1:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,佛罗明哥的那场秀越做越好罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That show at The Flamingo gets better and better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.35,1:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，山姆说 请你有空时打个电话给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}By the way, Sammy said whenever you have a minute, give him a call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.02,1:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-你也变传话的了啊？ -有钱我什么都做啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Made you a messenger, too? -I'll do anything for a buck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.69,1:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-他对每个人都这样，好好享用晚餐 -谢啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-He does it to everybody. Enjoy your dinner. -Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.19,1:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇最喜欢的 当然就是脱衣舞娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: I got to tell you, the thing Nicky liked most was the showgirls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.03,1:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对她们来说，尼奇像是电影名星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}To them, Nicky was the movie star.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.24,1:04:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-你就这样走过？ -这是雪莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You walk past me? -This is Shelly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.20,1:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨，雪莉，你好吗？ -嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Hi, Shelly. How are you? -Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.25,1:04:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是史黛希\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This is Stacy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.04,1:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是尼克，想吃晚餐吗？一起吧 -好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-This is Nick. Wanna have dinner? Come on. -All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.21,1:04:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去厨房看看 失陪一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let's check the kitchen first. Excuse us one second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.80,1:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，我带你去 我每天都空运新鲜的东西进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Come on, I'll show you. I fly stuff in fresh every day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.43,1:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我从老家运面包 从加州运鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I get bread from back home. I get fish from California.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.81,1:04:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,光从我们用奶喂食的小牛肉就看得出 我们绝对是好餐厅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You can always tell a great kitchen like ours because of the milk-fed veal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.60,1:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是诀窍 奶喂小牛的肉是纯白色的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's the secret. See, milk-fed veal is pure white.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.61,1:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其他餐馆都用那种粉红色的小牛肉 过去点，甜心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Out here, they got that pink veal. Slide over, honey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.90,1:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,粉红色的那种小牛肉 你就算是追个两天两夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now, pink veal you can pound for two days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.24,1:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它还是不会变嫩 你懂我的意思吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: It'll never ever get tender. You know what I mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.79,1:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我从这儿拿钱离开时 在街上被抢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}AL: I left here with the money. Got muscled on the street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.92,1:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是几个我欠钱的家伙 所以我把钱给他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}A couple guys, I owe them. So I gave them the money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.25,1:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-就是这样 -是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-That's what I did. -Yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.63,1:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你还敢自称是男人吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You call yourself a man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.47,1:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你是个撒谎的杂碎 他妈的烂赌的狗东西吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know you're a lying lowlife, motherfucking gambling degenerate prick?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.93,1:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己是什么东西吗？ 家里有两个小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know that's what you are? Two small kids at home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.77,1:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你钱付房租…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I gave you money to pay the fucking rent...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.81,1:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,买菜、开暖气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and buy groceries, put the heat on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.11,1:05:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你老婆打给法兰克 说家里连暖气都被停了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know your wife called Frankie and told him the fucking heat's off?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.61,1:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你没拿钱去赌吗？ 你敢这样跟我说吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You didn't gamble that money? Can you tell me that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.16,1:05:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没有吗？ -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-No, you didn't? -I didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.87,1:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别耍我，艾尔！ 别把我当傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't fuck with me, Al! Don't make a fuck out of me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.50,1:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你当我是傻子是吧？ 你没去赌？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You wanna make a fool out of me? You didn't gamble?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.87,1:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你把钱拿去赌掉了 我就给你钱回去交电费！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Tell me you gambled the money and I'll give you the money to put the heat on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.71,1:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有赌？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Did you gamble?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.72,1:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是他妈的狗东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Fucking degenerate, you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.18,1:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Fucking kids at home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.48,1:06:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去，给我滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Here. Get the fuck out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.36,1:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢了，尼克 -是啊，谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}AL: Thanks, Nick. NICKY: Yeah, thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.11,1:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,若被我知道是你搞砸的 我会把你扔在我找到你的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If I find out you fucked up, I'll leave you where I find you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.67,1:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要吃几个？ -两个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: How many of these you gonna eat? NICKY JR.: Two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.05,1:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但早上六点半，当他下班时…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: At around 6:30 a.m., when he finished his day...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.97,1:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他在那里或是在做什么…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}no matter where he was or what he was doing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.22,1:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他都会回家为儿子，小尼奇做早餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}he always went home to make breakfast for his son, Nicky boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.81,1:06:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I know you like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.98,1:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一点点牛油，对不对？ 不要很多，你知道为什么，对不对？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: A little butter, right? Not a lot. You know why, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.77,1:06:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？ -因为会堵塞心脏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Why? NICKY JR.: 'Cause it clogs up your heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.86,1:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是聪明的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What a smart kid you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.86,1:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Okay, eat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.16,1:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每隔几个礼拜我就会派玛雷诺 去老大那儿…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Every couple of weeks, I sent Marino back to the bosses...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.20,1:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也分他们一份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}with a piece of what I made.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.50,1:06:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是很多，但他们哪知道？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Not a big piece, but what did they know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.33,1:06:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在2500里外，天高皇帝远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They were 1,500 miles away, and I don't know anybody who can see that far.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.42,1:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,收货地点是个修车场…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Their drop was a truck stop garage...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.30,1:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,利蒙他们以前常在那儿数钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}where Remo and the guys used to hang out and count their millions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.39,1:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,条子们也知道，但他们不在乎 他们早协议好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The cops knew, but they didn't give a fuck. They worked it out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.52,1:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇向你们问好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky sends his warmest regards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.48,1:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道怎样让老大们服服帖帖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I knew how to keep the bosses happy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.60,1:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,每当他们有些小事需要我做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Whenever they gave me little jobs to do,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.59,1:07:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,例如传个话之类的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}you know, to send a message...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.11,1:07:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定做到完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I would carry things out to a "T."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.03,1:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那次东尼道格 那个听说是城里的新硬汉…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Like the time Tony Dogs, who was supposed to be the new maniac tough guy in town...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.20,1:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在利蒙的一家酒吧乱开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}shot up one of Remo's bars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.88,1:07:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这浑蛋打死了两个利蒙的手下…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Here's a fucking guy who kills two of Remo's guys...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.80,1:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个代班的倒霉女侍者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and a poor fucking waitress who was just working on her night off.{\r}
