Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.49,1:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你想偷吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You want to steal it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.45,1:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不，只是好奇 我是在想…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}No. I'm just curious. I was wondering...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.71,1:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他会在那种东西里 投入多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}how much he would put into a thing like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.25,1:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我说大约一百万 可能更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm told it's worth about $1 million, maybe more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.38,1:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是罗 这说明了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: There you go. What does that tell you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.72,1:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一百万的珠宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}$1 million in jewelry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.89,1:18:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这不说明了他爱你爱到疯了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Does that tell you he is crazy about you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.10,1:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本就不该嫁给他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I should have never married him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.73,1:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他是双子座的，双子加三级，两面人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's a Gemini. Triple Gemini. Duality.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.02,1:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,双子座就像条蛇 你不能相信蛇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Gemini is the snake, you know. You can't trust a snake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.15,1:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I mean it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.49,1:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂你的意思，金吉儿，听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I know what you mean. Listen, Ginger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.29,1:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能不是… 我也没有答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}This is probably not.... I don't have the answers anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.12,1:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-这可能不是你想听的 -我想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-This is probably not what you want to hear. -I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.46,1:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你不高兴，我可以理解…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're a little upset, and I understand that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.26,1:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但先撑着点吧 慢慢来，看看会发生什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But try to make the best of it now. Go slow. See what happens.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.59,1:19:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他差点杀了他！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He could've killed him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.60,1:19:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他用不着打他 我又没跟他上床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He didn't have to hit him. I'm not sleeping with the guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.85,1:19:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我得偷偷摸摸的 跟我的朋友见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He makes me sneak around to see my own friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.15,1:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What the fuck is that all about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.61,1:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是因为他太爱你了吧 他吃醋又担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I guess it's 'cause he loves you so much, he's jealous and worries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.45,1:19:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会在乎我做什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Who gives a fuck what I do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.20,1:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我会试着问问到底怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll try to find out what the hell is going on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.62,1:19:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-遇到他时我会跟他谈谈的 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-When I see him, I'll talk to him. -Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.29,1:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以吗？ -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-All right? -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.21,1:19:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thanks...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.51,1:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,忍受我唠叨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}for putting up with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.22,1:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,别喝这么凶吧 这只会让情况更糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Take it easy with this shit. This can only make matters worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.93,1:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个美女，别搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're a beautiful girl. Don't ruin that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.97,1:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过太多漂亮女孩 因这个变丑八怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I've seen a lot of girls get shot to hell from this stuff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.98,1:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're so nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.98,1:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了啦 我不想见你不快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Come on, now. I don't wanna see you unhappy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.40,1:19:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.33,1:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没事啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.97,1:20:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,县辅导派特委布来见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}County Commissioner Pat Webb is here to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.43,1:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-等一下 -好的，请稍候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Give me a minute. -Okay. Just a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.38,1:20:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}RECEPTIONIST: Can I get you anything?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.96,1:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不，谢谢，小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, thank you, little lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.22,1:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,让他进来，然后四分钟后打给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Send him in and call me four minutes after.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.88,1:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯坦先生，我是派特委布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Rothstein, I'm Pat Webb.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.22,1:20:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}How do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.31,1:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-幸会 -我常听起你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-It is a pleasure. -I heard a lot about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.43,1:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,过奖了，庄家最近还过得去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}PAT: Thank you, sir. House is doing well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.06,1:21:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那么多钱滚滚而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}All that money is rolling in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.40,1:21:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感激你愿意见我这老公仆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I appreciate you taking the time to see a poor old civil servant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.49,1:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-不如坐下吧？ -谢谢您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Why don't you have a seat? PAT: Thank you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.03,1:21:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来亲自化解…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}PAT: I come here personally to smooth over...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.33,1:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一些小误会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}any fracas about a certain matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.92,1:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能不知道…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Maybe you didn't know it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.79,1:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但道恩华德在镇上挺受欢迎的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but Don Ward is a very well-liked man in this town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.05,1:21:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他有许多朋友 他们家族及产业也很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's got lots of friends. His family and their money go back many years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.64,1:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友是选民 家人与金钱都能助选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Friends vote, family and money votes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.27,1:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你我都很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's important to me and you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.27,1:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,若你从这个角度 来看我们这个小问题的话…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If you'll think about our little problem along them lines...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.86,1:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我得这么说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and you'll forgive me for saying it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.07,1:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但他可能不该被开除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}maybe he did not deserve to be fired.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.62,1:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他非常清楚我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He knew about our getting hit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.62,1:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在一瞬间被赢了三个大奖 但他却袖手旁观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}on three big machines in a row, and he did nothing about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.79,1:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他要不是跟他们一伙 那很抱歉，他就是蠢到看不见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Either he was in on it or, forgive me, he was too dumb to see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.80,1:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不论如何，我都无法让一个 这样的人在这儿工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Either way, I cannot have a man like that working here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.30,1:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在将过错都推给道恩前…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Before we point the dirty end of the stick at old Don...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.84,1:22:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得先确定有证据这样指控他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}we better be sure we can prove them charges.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.56,1:22:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我，要是有证据 他早就被逮捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Believe me, if I could prove it, he'd be under arrest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.69,1:22:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定要让赌博游乐委员会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Are we certain that you want the Gaming Control Board...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.57,1:22:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,过目你与你的帮派朋友 尼奇的记录吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}eyeballing your record and your gangster pals like Nicky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.16,1:22:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你这样跟我说 有点太过份了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I think you're way out of line talking to me like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.83,1:22:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你所说的几乎是毁谤 你无权怀疑我的专业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What you're saying is libelous. You're in no position to challenge my expertise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.37,1:22:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我已尽我所能去 帮助并善待那孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I went way out of my way to be helpful and courteous to that kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.84,1:22:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他太弱了也很无能 他使这地方濒于险境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's weak. He's incompetent. He jeopardizes the whole place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.34,1:22:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我对他真的无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}There's not much more I can do for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.51,1:22:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You have got me there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.35,1:22:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,道恩就像公猪身上的奶头一样无用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Old Don is as useless as tits on a boar.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.89,1:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但他还是我的小舅子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But he is my brother-in-law...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.61,1:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会当是我欠你的一个人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and I would look on it as a personal favor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.36,1:22:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,若你愿意考虑重新聘用他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}if you'd think some more on hiring him back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.53,1:22:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can't do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.70,1:22:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他是你的小舅子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I appreciate the fact that he's your brother-in-law.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.41,1:22:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想帮你更喜欢卖人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I do want to help you and I like to do favors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.79,1:22:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道你的地位 但我真的不能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And I know who you are. But I cannot do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.42,1:23:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,日后是否会有其它较适合的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Could there be any position...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.47,1:23:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,职位呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}farther down the trough?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.81,1:23:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，并没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm sorry. I can't do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.22,1:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他太无能了 最终还是他不能被信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's too incompetent. The bottom line is he cannot be trusted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.94,1:23:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Okay, thanks a lot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.70,1:23:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's it. I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.12,1:23:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯坦先生 你们这帮人永远都不会懂…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Rothstein, your people never will understand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.29,1:23:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的世界如何运作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the way it works out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.42,1:23:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们只不过来此地做客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're all just our guests.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.13,1:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但却喧宝夺主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But you act like you're at home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.30,1:23:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让我告诉你，老兄 这并不是你家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let me tell you something, partner. You ain't home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.30,1:23:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,家是我们州长生气时 送你们回的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But that's where we'll send you if it harelips the Governor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.64,1:23:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-多谢你空出时间见我 -没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Thank you for your time. -No problem.{\r}
