Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.28,1:38:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇的名字布满每家报纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky's name was in every newspaper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.24,1:38:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇因为一堆谋杀案调查被侦讯 但他们每次都放他走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky was questioned in two dozen murders, but they always had to let him go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.16,1:38:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没有目击者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}There were never any witnesses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.58,1:38:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,条子把所有的不顺 都归昝于我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: The coppers blamed me for everything that went wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.17,1:38:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点 你会好看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Watch yourself. You're gonna get runned over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.96,1:38:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,若有个家伙踩到香蕉皮跌倒 可能都要带我回局里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: If a guy tripped over a banana peel, they'd bring me in for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.59,1:38:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,客气点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Be nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.14,1:38:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,老大们也没好到哪儿去 他们抱怨事情运作不顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: The bosses were no better. They complained because things don't run smooth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.43,1:38:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不过在我这行 真抱歉，事情本来就不会顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}In my line of work, things don't run so smooth. I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.77,1:38:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天对付的可是些三教九流之徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'm dealing with degenerate animals out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.15,1:38:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老大们在乎个屁啊？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The bosses, what do they give a fuck?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.28,1:38:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只会坐着喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They're sitting on their asses drinking anisette.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.61,1:38:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而这期间我得做牛做马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Meanwhile, I'm the guy in the trenches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.95,1:38:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那些王八老大们 真以为天下的午餐都是免费的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Fucking bosses think it's a fucking free lunch out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.29,1:38:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰克，他们在沙漠里 找到一个家伙的头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Frankie, they found a guy's head in the desert.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.96,1:38:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know about that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.83,1:39:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I heard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.59,1:39:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在讲，报纸里也有登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Everybody's talking about it and making a big deal out of it. It's in all the papers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.76,1:39:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What are you gonna do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.47,1:39:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That's no good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.89,1:39:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他做事要小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Tell him to take care of things a little better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.89,1:39:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的，利蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll tell him, Remo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.14,1:39:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,王八老大们抽着雪茄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Fucking bosses smoking their Di Nobilis...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.98,1:39:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,吃着他们的美食…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and eating trip' and fucking soffrit', fried pigs' guts...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.32,1:39:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而我若想私下找人谈话 我还得坐在公车站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}while if I wanna talk private, I gotta go to a fucking bus stop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.82,1:39:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们在乎个屁？只要我拿钱回去 -他们在抱怨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-What do they care? Long as I send money. -They're complaining.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.28,1:39:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们抱怨，是我在这儿 活都是我在做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let them complain. I'm the one who's here. I do all the work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.20,1:39:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-有人不喜欢，就去他的 -你决定罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Somebody don't like it, fuck them. FRANK: It's up to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.63,1:39:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们他妈的想打仗？ 我准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: They want a fucking war? I'm ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.21,1:39:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要干掉那五个 其他的自然会水到渠成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If I take care of five of those guys, the rest will fall into place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.84,1:39:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,被我抓到了吧，这群王八羔子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: Peek-a-boo, you fucks, you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.06,1:39:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你们了，浑蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I see you, you motherfuckers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.93,1:39:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是，尼奇不只是 让自己更受注目，还连累到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Nicky was not only bringing heat on himself, but on me, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.69,1:40:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局盯着他的每一步 但他不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The FBI watched every move he made, but he just didn't care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.36,1:40:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想要盯我，我就盯回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: If they're gonna watch me, I'm gonna watch them back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.40,1:40:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,或许花了很多钱 但谁在乎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I spent a few bucks. Top dollar. Who gives a shit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.45,1:40:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我买了最先进的反窃听装置 向卖给中央调查局的那家买的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I got the latest anti-bugging equipment from the same places that sell to the CIA.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.08,1:40:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我有所有的警察特殊频道对讲机 FBI的解干扰器、夜光照相机…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I had all the special police frequency radios, FBI de-scramblers, night-vision cameras....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.88,1:40:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这些衰角从未抓到我任何把柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}So, the miserable sons of bitches never caught me doing anything I couldn't handle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.38,1:40:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我工作都快丢了 但他却玩得不亦乐乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: I got my job on the line, he's having the time of his life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.76,1:40:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全州的警察都在盯他 他却在打高尔夫球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He has every cop in the state watching him, and he's out playing golf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.85,1:40:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说时期最坏不过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And at the worst possible time for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.23,1:40:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我的执照听证会要到了 我不想有一点点失败的机率\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I had my license hearing coming up and I didn't want to leave anything to chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.98,1:40:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,若不能在赌城工作 那我要去哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If I can't work in Vegas, where am I gonna go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.32,1:40:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都很合作 从文件到帐簿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You've been very open with us with the books and papers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.03,1:40:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这对委员会是很重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}That'll mean a lot when you go before the commission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.66,1:40:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只希望能有个公正的听证会 -你的诚实会为你赢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-All I ask is a fair hearing. -This honesty will guarantee it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.91,1:40:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}We'll move on to....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.04,1:40:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听听关于堪萨斯市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: I want to hear about Kansas City.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.26,1:41:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈的是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What the fuck is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.30,1:41:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙要停在哪里，球场上吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Where's this fucking guy gonna land, in the fairway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.08,1:41:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是探员，法兰克 来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They're fucking agents, Frankie. Look at this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.46,1:41:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们盯尼奇打高尔夫盯到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: The Feds were watching Nicky play golf for so long...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.17,1:41:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机没油\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}they ran out of gas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.92,1:41:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是我需要的 就在委员会面前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Just what I needed, right in front of the control board.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.89,1:41:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赌一百看谁先打到飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}$100, whoever hits the plane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.85,1:41:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,祸不单行，随后就看到派斯康 堪萨斯市的老二\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: If things weren't bad enough... in comes Piscano, the Kansas City underboss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.32,1:41:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在堪萨斯市收皮箱的那家超市 就是他开的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He ran the grocery store in Kansas City where they brought the suitcases.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.94,1:42:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,又在为皮箱的事吵了 你知道这代表什么吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Fighting over those suitcases again. You know what that means?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.28,1:42:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我又得去拉斯维加斯了 又要花我好几千\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I gotta take another trip to Vegas. It's gonna cost me another couple grand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.95,1:42:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他和他姐夫一起开店…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: He ran it with his brother-in-law...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.54,1:42:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但他大多都在跟他姐夫与岳母 抱怨他去赌城的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but he mostly complained about his trips to Vegas to his brother-in-law and mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.04,1:42:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你得表明态度 要不然他们当你是病猫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You gotta lay down the law, or they'll make a fool out of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.59,1:42:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我全记下来了，他妈的每一分一毛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I write it all down. Every fucking nickel goes down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.26,1:42:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是怎么了？ -全都在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-What's the matter with you? -Everything's here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.01,1:42:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-你何时开始这样讲话？ -抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Since when do you talk like that? -I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.14,1:42:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,南斯要是找我麻烦 我就将他的眼挖出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nance gives me trouble, I'll take the eyes out of his freaking head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.73,1:42:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-又来了 -我没骂粗话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Again. -I didn't curse, I said, "freaking head."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.19,1:42:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-够了 -抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-That's enough. -I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.48,1:42:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来发生的事 简直是出乎意料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: What happens next, you can't believe it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.78,1:42:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会想到联邦调查局 会在里面装窃听器…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Who'd believe the FBI had a wire in the place...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.70,1:42:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为了调查很久以前的一桩命案…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}looking for information about some old homicide...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.45,1:42:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为了一个不知在何时 也不知为何事被干掉的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}about some guy who was whacked out God knows when over God knows what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.87,1:42:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么阻止拿皮箱的人 拿走他想要的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What prevents him with the suitcases from taking what he wants?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.00,1:42:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,南斯从坦吉乐拿了两口箱子回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nance brings back two suitcases from the Tangiers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.25,1:42:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,若其实有三箱或四箱呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What about three or four?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.04,1:42:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有人在计算室里看着 那是法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}We've got nobody in the room to watch. That's the law.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.05,1:42:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们甚至连计算室都进不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}We can't even go into the count room to watch our money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.76,1:43:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他有他的人在里面 他们搞不好根本是一伙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's got his people in there. They could all be in on it together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.10,1:43:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,若我知道是葛林干的 我会埋了那王八蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll find out. If it's Green himself, I'll bury that bastard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.39,1:43:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我从就不相信他 我后脑都有眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I never trusted him. I got eyes behind my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.06,1:43:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们信任那浑蛋，我可不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They trust that scumbag. I don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.86,1:43:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我该给他们一人一铲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll hit the two of them in the head with a shovel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.28,1:43:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}MA: Take it easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.44,1:43:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妈，抱歉 但他们一直跟我玩阴的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Ma, I'm sorry. They're beating me left and right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.32,1:43:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-抱歉，我很生气 -我知道，可是够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ARTIE: I'm sorry. I'm upset. I know, but that's enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.74,1:43:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道他们在对我做什么 我受不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know what they're doing to me. I can't take this no more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.04,1:43:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷静，别心脏病发 -我知道，我太气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}MA: Take it easy. You'll get a heart attack. ARTIE: I know. I'm too upset.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.92,1:43:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的是，他们听得一清二楚…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: The damn thing is, they hear all this stuff...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.21,1:43:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,关于拉斯维加斯，赌场还有皮箱…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}about Las Vegas, casinos, and suitcases...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.59,1:43:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,玩完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and that's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.72,1:43:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是从我口袋里掏 我得付钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ARTIE: Everything's coming out of my pocket. I gotta pay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.89,1:43:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信有这么巧吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Would you believe this could happen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.60,1:43:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,华府
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.98,1:43:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来赚钱的，不是亏钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ARTIE: I'm in this to make money, not lose it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.98,1:43:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全国每个联邦调查局探员 都张大了耳朵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Every FBI man across the country had their ears open now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.82,1:43:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要将事情办好就得靠自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ARTIE: If you want something done right you gotta do it yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.87,1:44:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,派司康这家伙 几乎搞砸了所有人的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Piscano, this guy, basically sunk the whole world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.83,1:44:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有些好的就有些坏的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}MA: There are some that are good and some that are bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.79,1:44:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1980年
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.88,1:44:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生 委员会的同仁…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}COUNSELOR: Members of the Commission...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.84,1:44:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今天罗斯坦先生很荣幸能在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Rothstein is pleased to be here today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.84,1:44:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,当那天终于来时 我已准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: When the day finally came, I was ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.30,1:44:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我自信满满的认为 我只需要呈上我的案件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I felt so confident that all I had to do was present my case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.22,1:44:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拥有文件，其中一份是由 一位退休的联邦探员写的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}COUNSELOR: We have documents, one of which is a report by retired FBl agents...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.81,1:44:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上头清楚的记载罗斯坦先生 并未触犯任何法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}which completely absolves Mr. Rothstein from any wrongdoing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.23,1:44:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-律师，在你继续前… -我要将这呈为…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Counselor, before you continue... -I want to have this marked....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.82,1:44:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,本委员会针对是否应 驳回罗斯坦的申请书在此动议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}...this Commission acts on a motion denying the Rothstein application.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.07,1:44:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-驳回？ -有人赞成驳回吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}COUNSELOR: Denying? SENATOR: Do I hear a motion seconded?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.20,1:44:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生，我赞成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Chairman, I second the motion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.99,1:44:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有赞同票吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Do I have a vote on the motion?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.74,1:44:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,同意！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Aye! -Aye!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.21,1:44:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,同意票获胜，听证会结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The ayes have it. This hearing is adjourned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.29,1:44:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-开什么玩笑 -什么叫结束？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You have to be kidding. -Adjourned? What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.25,1:44:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,议员，你答应我一场听证会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Senator, you promised me a hearing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.61,1:44:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你连联邦调查局的报告都没看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You didn't even look at the FBl reports.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.05,1:44:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你来坦吉乐作客时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}When you were my guest at the Tangiers Hotel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.96,1:44:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是答应我会有公平的听证会？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}didn't you promise me a fair hearing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.31,1:45:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-我从未是你的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SENATOR: I was never your guest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.72,1:45:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是我的客人？我没招待过你？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Never my guest? I never comped you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.98,1:45:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我一个月 没有最少招待你三次？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't comp you at least three times a month?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.40,1:45:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在回答这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'd like to answer that at this time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.82,1:45:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯坦先生的反应很常见 他在撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Rothstein is being very typical to this point. He's lying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.19,1:45:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一一次去过坦吉乐 就是巴尼葛林斯坦那次晚宴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The only time I was at the Tangiers was a dinner with Barney Greenstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.24,1:45:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-我当时在场吗？ -你四处周旋着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Was I at the dinner? SENATOR: You were wandering around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.03,1:45:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-我在场吗？ -你四处周旋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Was I at that dinner? SENATOR: You were wandering.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.16,1:45:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在室内 -我在室内？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SENATOR: You were in the building. SAM: I was in the building?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.29,1:45:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你很清楚我在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know damn well I was there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.01,1:45:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你向我保证会有公正的听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You swore I would have a fair hearing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.09,1:45:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Did you not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.88,1:45:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,至少承认说我那天在场 这总可以了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Tell me I was at least at the dinner. Allow me that much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.85,1:45:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-至少也得说我在场吧！ -是，你在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Give me that much at least! SENATOR: Yes, you were.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.43,1:45:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你没说我是骗子 你这个狗东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thanks for not calling me a liar, you son of a bitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.40,1:45:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一场例行的听证会 在昨晚成了一场闹剧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}A routine licensing hearing turned into bedlam yesterday...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.90,1:45:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当抢眼的坦吉乐高层 山姆“艾斯”罗斯坦…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}when the flamboyant Tangiers Casino executive, Sam "Ace" Rothstein...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.70,1:45:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,指控赌博游乐委员会高官贪污\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}accused top gaming officials of corruption.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.66,1:45:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你在我的旅馆接受招待 并答应我会有公平的听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}...promised me a fair hearing when you were comped at my hotel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.66,1:46:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要求将你的帐单挂公帐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And you asked for copies of your bill to put on your expense account.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.00,1:46:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当赌博游乐执照被驳回时大吼大叫…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}In a wild outburst that followed his gaming license denial...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.38,1:46:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-狗屁！ -罗斯坦与好几名…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Bullshit! ...Rothstein followed several...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.71,1:46:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,错愕的委员到走道 并持续着他的指控…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}stunned commissioners into the hallway where he continued his harangue...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.26,1:46:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,直到他的律师与朋友劝他离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}until his own lawyers and friends urged him to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.89,1:46:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有过去，我也有过去 我的不见得比你的糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You have a past. I have a past. My past is no worse than yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.14,1:46:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还自以为有权去判决别人！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You guys think you have the right to pass judgment!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.02,1:46:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被怀疑长期无照管理坦吉乐…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NEWSREADER: Long suspected of running Tangiers without a license...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.23,1:46:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的听证会本是要决议 像罗斯坦如此背景的人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}yesterday's hearing was to determine if someone with Rothstein's history...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.82,1:46:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有资格正式在赌博游乐界 担任如此高的职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}was qualified to officially hold a top gaming post.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.78,1:46:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯坦玩完了 王八伪君子！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}REMO: Fucking hypocrites!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.53,1:46:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-他现在怎么办？ -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-What the hell's he gonna do now? -I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.12,1:46:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他在干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What's he doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.87,1:46:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他也知道他大吼大叫的那群人 都是我们的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He knows all those guys he yelled at are friends of ours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.79,1:46:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎么了，搞得一团糟？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What's the matter with him, making all this mess?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.13,1:46:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他或许可以用另一个头衔管事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Maybe he could run things with another job title.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.63,1:46:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是最好的 但我们又能如何呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Won't be the best, but what are we gonna do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.34,1:46:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他不论管什么，都得安静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}REMO: However he runs things, it's gotta be quiet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.34,1:46:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,让他躲到楼上办公室去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let him hide upstairs in the office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.72,1:46:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说他是工友，我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Say he's a janitor. I don't give a shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.97,1:47:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但拜托，不管他做什么 都得低调点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But please, whatever job he takes, make sure it's something quiet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.91,1:47:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,各位先生与女士…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ANNOUNCER: [On TV] Ladies and gentlemen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.37,1:47:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,坦吉乐大饭店 非常荣幸能为您介绍…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the Tangiers Hotel proudly presents the all-new...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.33,1:47:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆罗斯坦秀，   《艾斯的单人牌》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Sam Rothstein show, Aces High.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.16,1:47:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,艾斯的单人牌
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.96,1:47:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚，从最新的球赛赌区 现场实况转播…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Tonight, taped live from the all-new sports book...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.92,1:47:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为您带来《艾斯的单人牌》的 首次演出…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}we present the premiere showing of Aces High...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.05,1:47:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,连同莎夏西门诺夫交响乐团…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}with the Sasha Semenoff Orchestra...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.84,1:47:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,与山姆罗斯坦舞群！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and the Sam Rothstein dancers!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.18,1:47:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯坦先生是位职业赌徒 也是全美最棒的美式足球下注者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Rothstein is a professional gambler and the best U.S. football handicapper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.23,1:47:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一位能带领你进入 真正的拉斯维加斯的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}A man who will take you inside the real Las Vegas as no one has ever done before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.36,1:47:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在让我们欢迎 坦吉乐赌场新的娱乐董事…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Now, the new entertainment director of the Tangiers Hotel Casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.91,1:47:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆罗斯坦先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Mr. Sam Rothstein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.00,1:48:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到山姆罗斯坦秀 很高兴你们能参与\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Welcome to the Sam Rothstein show. We're happy to have you here this evening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.51,1:48:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我左边的这位小姐是特茹蒂…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The young lady to my left is Trudy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.47,1:48:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我们巴黎秀新的首席舞者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}who is a lead new dancer in our fabulous show from Paris.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.85,1:48:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚的第一位来宝…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Our first guest this evening...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.56,1:48:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰克艾华伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}is Frankie Avalon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.82,1:48:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-看好他 -我有个大家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}PAT: Keep an eye on him. FRANKIE: I've got a large family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.28,1:48:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有几个孩子？ -我很自豪的说，八个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: How many kids do you have? I'm very proud to say, eight children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.00,1:48:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-太了不起了 -没什么，是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-That's amazing. -There's nothing to it. It was my pleasure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.38,1:48:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}PHILIP: Ace, don't do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.51,1:48:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Jesus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.43,1:48:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他在耍杂技！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's juggling!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.18,1:48:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们别对县辅导 派特委布太认真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Let's not take County Commissioner Pat Webb too seriously.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.18,1:48:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近本想邀他在节目上辩论的 但是他拒绝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I recently challenged him to a debate on this program, and he declined.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.94,1:48:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在担心什么呢，派特？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What are you worried about, Pat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.03,1:49:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要事先给我问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You don't have to send me any questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.19,1:49:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都可以问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You can ask me anything you want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.32,1:49:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他在电视上干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ANDY: What the hell is he doing on television?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.70,1:49:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他整晚都在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's on all night,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.75,1:49:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喊着要将他的案子告上最高法院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}screaming about taking his lawsuit to the Supreme Court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.58,1:49:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是疯了 他想将这带到华府去？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He really must be crazy. He's gonna go to Washington with this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.63,1:49:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他简直是疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's out of his fucking mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.21,1:49:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,世上有这样的伪君子真是可叹 他们爱做什么就做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's a pity we have such hypocrisy. Some people do what they want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.13,1:49:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人却得承担后果 这就是人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Other people have to pay through the nose. Such is life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.26,1:49:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪，去找他 告诉他辞职的时候到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Andy, go see him. Tell him maybe it's time he should quit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.27,1:49:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,第一点，他们的所做所为 完全的违反了宪法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: First, what they did was totally unconstitutional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.15,1:49:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已在高等法院的等候单上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: We're on the list to be heard before the U.S. Supreme Court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.90,1:49:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙才不在乎高等法院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}These guys don't care about the Supreme Court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.32,1:49:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要一切平息，要你别再搞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They want things to quiet down. They want you to walk away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.80,1:49:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别搞了？安迪，\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Walk away? Andy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.61,1:49:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说真的 你难道看不到这严重性吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}you can't be serious. Don't you see what's at stake?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.33,1:49:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老头说你的朋友或许该罢手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The old man said maybe your friend should give in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.34,1:49:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,当老头说“或许”时 就像是教皇发谕令一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}When the old man says "maybe," that's like a papal bull.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.30,1:50:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不但该罢手，还该跑路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Not only should you quit, you should run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.17,1:50:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们每次在报上提到我的名字 就一定扯到尼奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Every time they mention my name in the papers, they mention Nicky, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.68,1:50:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈的有什么帮助？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}How the fuck does that help?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.35,1:50:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他带来的注目简直是谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The heat he brought down is murder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.64,1:50:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,警察局本来很合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The police department was cooperative.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.69,1:50:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他将他们激怒到 现在大家都动不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}They're pissed off. Nobody can make a move anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.48,1:50:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能怎样呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What do you do about that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.86,1:50:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想说什么？ -我不知道，他根本不听我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-What are you proposing? -I don't know. He doesn't listen to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.15,1:50:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他才该消失一阵子 这样会很糟吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Maybe he should get lost for a while. Would that be so bad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.95,1:50:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们不会调走尼奇的 -若他离开一阵…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-They ain't sending Nicky nowhere. -If he took a break...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.62,1:50:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给大家移动布局的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}it would give everybody time to maneuver.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.87,1:50:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别再搞布局的事 赶紧离开吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I would forget about the maneuver. I would just get out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.88,1:50:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I can't do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.21,1:50:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，安迪一到家后 尼奇就听说我们的谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Of course, as soon as Andy got home, Nicky heard about our talk in the car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.64,1:50:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天一大早，我就接到电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Next morning, bright and early, I get the call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.47,1:50:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去买点东西，你要不要去？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I've got to do some shopping. Want to go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.89,1:50:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,连接尼奇的电话都不是件易事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Getting a call from Nicky wasn't easy anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.56,1:50:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,暗号都没有用了 我们得想新方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Even the codes didn't work. So we figured out another act.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.08,1:50:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,若是电话被窃听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}If a phone's tapped,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.64,1:50:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只能听关于犯罪的谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}the Feds can only listen in on the stuff involving crimes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.07,1:51:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,例行通话时 他们必须在几分钟后挂断\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}On routine calls, they have to click off after a few minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.66,1:51:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我手肘好像扭到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: I got a sprained fucking elbow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.87,1:51:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,三点见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Meet me at 3:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.25,1:51:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-在凯撒宫吗？ -这条路下去再一百码处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-At Caesar's? -100 yards further down the road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.58,1:51:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？ -别问了，到那儿就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Why? -Don't ask questions. Just be there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.13,1:51:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,苏西克理姆有件一模一样的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Suzy Cream Cheese has the same outfit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.59,1:51:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到个东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: I saw something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.09,1:51:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西好可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Something very cute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.26,1:51:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他出门了，棕组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}AGENT: Okay, he's out. It's the ant. Brown unit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.27,1:51:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他带着个替身，应该是法兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's with the bogey. I think it's Frankie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.19,1:51:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇比我早出门…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Nicky started out before me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.19,1:51:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他要出门越来越难了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}because it wasn't that easy for him to get around anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.65,1:51:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,尼奇到那儿都最起码得…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Nicky couldn't even go for a ride without changing cars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.49,1:51:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,换六次车才甩得掉跟踪他的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}at least six times before he could shake all his tails.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.45,1:51:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有飞机 所以他得用地下停车场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Because of the planes, he had to use underground garages.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.16,1:52:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在沙漠中央会面总让我紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Meeting in the desert always made me nervous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.91,1:52:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个可怕的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's a scary place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.66,1:52:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然也知道沙漠里的洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I knew about the holes in the desert, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.87,1:52:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我张望的每一处都可能是个洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And everywhere I looked, there could have been a hole.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.30,1:52:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,通常我与尼奇会面 能活着回来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Normally, my prospects of coming back alive...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.55,1:52:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,机率是百分之九十九\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}from a meeting with Nicky were 99 out of 100.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.14,1:52:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次，当我听他说 离道路几百码外…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But this time, when I heard him say a couple of hundred yards down the road...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.89,1:52:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想应该还有一半的机率吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I gave myself 50-50.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.21,1:53:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的跟别人 在背后捅我是什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Where the fuck you get off talking to people behind my back?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.21,1:53:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-跟什么人？ -你以为我不会发现吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-What people? -Did you think I wouldn't find out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.97,1:53:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本不知道你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I don't even know what you're talking about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.30,1:53:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我害你被盯？ 我得因为你被人家念？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You said I'm bringing heat on you? I gotta listen to people because of you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.39,1:53:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你想搞走我？ 你最好准备好自己的军队？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're ordering me out? You better get your own fucking army!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.56,1:53:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有要搞走任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I didn't order you or anybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.40,1:53:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟安迪说你被盯上了 这是个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I told Andy Stone that you had heat, and that was a problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.23,1:53:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我离开我自己的地盘？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You want me to get out of my own fucking town?{\r}
