Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.82,2:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他晚上根本不回家 有什么了不起？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He doesn't come home at night. What is the big fucking deal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.74,2:10:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我走，听着，我真的受不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I go.... Listen, I just can't fucking take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.41,2:10:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要忍受？ 这不是我们的协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Why should I fucking take it? That wasn't the deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.91,2:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他一副好像就只有我有过去的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He acts like I'm the only one around here with a fucking past.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.45,2:10:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他永远都不让我忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He'll never let me live it down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.67,2:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我试过，我当然试过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Well, yes, I have tried. Of course I've tried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.75,2:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我为什么回来？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}What the fuck do you think I came back here for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.00,2:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我不，我想杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, I'm not. I want to have him killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:26.59,2:10:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我要杀了他 我受够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: I want him killed. I've had it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.88,2:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你要帮我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}So are you with me on this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:32.68,2:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干掉我？我就在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You want to get rid of me? Here I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:35.77,2:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊，干掉我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Go ahead. Get rid of me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.35,2:10:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-喂 -是的！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Hello. GINGER: Yes, I do!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.40,2:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨死你了！我受不了了！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: I fucking hate you! I can't take it anymore!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.19,2:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我要杀了你！ 我恨死你了！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, I want to kill you! I hate your fucking guts!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.11,2:10:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你恨死我了？ 我要你现在就给我过来！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: You hate my guts? I want you to come with me now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.29,2:10:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你滚！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: I want you out of here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.71,2:11:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拿好行李给我滚！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Take your fucking bag and get out of here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.67,2:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我会走，但我现在就要我的钱！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'll go, but I want my money right now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.88,2:11:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-你会拿到钱的！别担心 -协议结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-You'll get your money! Don't worry. -The arrangement is over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.84,2:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-废话！ -我还是拿得到钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: No kidding! GINGER: And I still get my money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:14.60,2:11:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就要一些现金 你不能就这样把我赶出街！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I need some cash now! You can't just put me in the street!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.77,2:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你从一认识我就没诚实过！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You've never been straight with me ever since I met you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.40,2:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你从一开始就没爱过我！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You never even loved me in the first place!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.65,2:11:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你这婊子一起 我连脑后都得长眼睛！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I need eyes in the back of my head with you, you bitch!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.48,2:11:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么爱你？ 你对我像对条狗一样！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}How could I love you? You treat me like I'm your fucking dog!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.82,2:11:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-你连狗都不如！ -去你的！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: You're lower than a dog! GINGER: Fuck you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.62,2:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去！够了没？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Here! Is this enough money?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.45,2:11:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以活两天吗？拿去！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Will it last you two fucking days? Take it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.33,2:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-贪得无厌的婊子，钱拿去 -我要去银行…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Greedy bitch. Take the fucking money. -I'm going to the bank...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.50,2:11:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-我还要去拿我的珠宝！ -早上9点开，去拿啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-and I'm getting my jewelry, too! -It opens at 9:00 a.m. Be there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.00,2:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫你的人去阻止我！ 我说真的！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Don't send your guys down there to stop me! I mean it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.17,2:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证我绝对不会阻止你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I guarantee you, I will not stop you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.22,2:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你别想以一口箱子就打发我！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're not getting rid of me with one fucking suitcase!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.01,2:11:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的明天再回来拿吧 给我滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Come back tomorrow and get the rest. Just get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.39,2:11:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要带艾美走 -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: I'm taking Amy. SAM: You're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.22,2:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要，我现在去叫她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I am. I'm waking her up right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.81,2:12:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你剋药了，你这个毒虫 给我滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: You're stoned. You're a junkie. Get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:01.02,2:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是！她也是我女儿！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I am not! She's my daughter, too!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.98,2:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,写信给我的律师吧，去你的！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Send my lawyers a letter, god-fucking-damn you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:06.23,2:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你跑不掉的！ 你别想不遵守你的诺言！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: You're not getting away with this! You're not gonna cut me out of my end!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.53,2:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,王八蛋！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}GINGER: Fucker!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:05.08,2:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好笑的是，经过这么多事 我还是不想让她走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: The funny thing was, after all that, I didn't want her to go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:09.09,2:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我孩子的妈，我爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}She was the mother of my kid. I loved her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.92,2:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,后来，\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Later,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.43,2:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现我并不想 将钱给她，因为我若给了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I realized I didn't want to give her the money because if I did...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:17.51,2:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道将再也见不到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I knew I'd never see her again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.36,2:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在学校要开开心心的喔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Have a good day at school, okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:33.95,2:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Okay, angel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:40.33,2:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起，我随时都得知道 你与艾美在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}From now on, I have to know where you and Amy are at all times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.29,2:13:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是呼叫器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Here's a beeper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.59,2:13:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你拿着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I want you to keep it on you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.88,2:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很轻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's very light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.55,2:13:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,让我可以随时打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: So I can call you whenever I have to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.68,2:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:10.48,2:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你能怎么做？ 你想怎么做呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: What are you supposed to do? What do you wanna do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:12.49,2:14:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你想就像现在这样吗？ 你也不能啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You want to stay the way you are? You can't do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:15.41,2:14:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人若合不来 总要有人出来说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Two people don't get along, at some point you gotta call it....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.49,2:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这不关我的事 但我觉得你应该这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's not my business, but I think that's what you gotta do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.58,2:14:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对，我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're right. I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:23.58,2:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只是… -什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-I was just-- -What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.21,2:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-没什么 -你想说什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Nothing. -What were you gonna say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.00,2:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不… -告诉我你本来想说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-I don't-- -Tell me what you were gonna say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:31.30,2:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.34,2:14:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想说你有没有认识 银行的人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I was thinking maybe you know somebody at the bank...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.34,2:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可以帮我把珠宝拿出来？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}who could help me get my jewelry out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.93,2:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多钱在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}There's a lot of money in there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.18,2:14:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意重赏任何可以帮助我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I'd be willing to take care of anybody who helped me out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.02,2:14:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let me think about that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.82,2:14:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看能找谁 一定得是可以信得过的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Let me see who I got. Gotta get somebody I can trust.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.53,2:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道他是不会把珠宝给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You know he's never gonna give me my jewelry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:57.11,2:15:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他把那把钥匙抓得很紧 我看就差没藏到屁眼里去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He holds that key so tight, he's probably got it stuck up his ass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.12,2:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,说得好，真像是山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You're right. That's Sammy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.62,2:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好真的就在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}And he's probably got it there, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.67,2:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是命大，我本可以埋了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's so fucking lucky. I could have buried him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.42,2:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以去欧洲并把孩子带走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I could have gone to Europe and taken the baby.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.63,2:15:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那他可能就会找到我 并把我杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Then he'd have tracked me down, and he'd have killed me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.68,2:15:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不，他不会，但我会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}No, he wouldn't. I would have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:22.77,2:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-不过他是没错 -别闹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-He'd have been right, too. Seriously. -Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:25.81,2:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样把他的孩子带走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You don't take a guy's kid and then take off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.60,2:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有，我本来有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I didn't. I did,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:30.38,2:15:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但后来我照你所说的回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}but then I did exactly what you told me to do, and I came back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:32.90,2:15:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是，你照做了，很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You did. You're right. I like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.49,2:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-我喜欢这样，你做对了 -我听了你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-That's what I like, you did the right thing. -I did what you told me to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:40.83,2:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的 -你总会告诉我正确的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Yes, you did. -You always tell me the right thing to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.59,2:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的在这儿把自己搞砸了 不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He really fucked himself up out here, didn't he?{\r}
