Dialogue: 0,2:39:21.18,2:39:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们不能做什么 -你瞧瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-There's nothing we can do. -Look, look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:23.77,2:39:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不能抓她超速吗？ 看看她开多快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}You can't stop her for speeding? Look what she's doing.{\r}
