Dialogue: 0,2:39:31.11,2:39:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们在加油站拦她 -好的，就这么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Let's pull her over at that Citgo Station. -Okay. Let's do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:45.87,2:39:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们必须逮捕你 -为了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-We're placing you under arrest. -For what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:48.79,2:39:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-为了协助犯罪… -为了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-For aiding and abetting-- -For what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:52.04,2:39:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-为了协助犯罪… -我只是要离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-For aiding and abetting-- -I'm just trying to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:55.59,2:39:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这么多威胁之后…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: After all the threats and bullshit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:57.68,2:39:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,金吉儿什么都没告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}it turned out Ginger didn't tell them anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:39:59.80,2:40:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但那时，他们也不需要她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}But, by then, the Feds didn't need her anyway.{\r}
