Dialogue: 0,2:40:06.52,2:40:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-大家就像牌九一样跟着倒 -联邦调查局！我们有拘捕令！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Everyone began to tumble, like dominoes. FBI! We have a warrant!{\r}
