Dialogue: 0,2:40:14.40,2:40:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还是尼奇、我与我的执照…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}between Nicky, Ginger, me and my license...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:17.74,2:40:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂就这样被我们搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}paradise. We managed to really fuck it up.{\r}
