Dialogue: 0,2:40:24.95,2:40:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局，我们有搜查令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}FBI. We have a federal search warrant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:27.25,2:40:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上知道苗头不对 所以我跑路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: I got wind of the pinches coming down, so I took off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:30.42,2:40:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谁要待在那儿找麻烦啊？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Who needs to hang around for that bullshit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:32.46,2:40:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是马克凯斯伯，FBI -是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-I'm Mark Casper, FBI. -Yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:34.75,2:40:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以打个电话吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Can I make a fucking phone call?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:36.42,2:40:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以，但你不用这样对我们讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes, but you don't have to talk to us like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:39.01,2:40:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都出去 往警铃的方向走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}FBI AGENT: Everybody, out of the room. Over to the alarm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:42.10,2:40:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-其他人似乎都被抓了 -这地方被查封了！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: They got almost everybody else. FBI AGENT: This area is seized!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:45.93,2:40:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-去拿总户头单 -我要查封所有的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Get the master account list. -I want all those papers seized.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:40:53.44,2:40:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,将每个箱子都放到桌上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}FBI AGENT: Put every box on the table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:02.49,2:41:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好，在这儿，所有的数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Yes. Here we are. Little craps figures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:06.24,2:41:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,葛林？别提了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Green? Don't even ask.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:07.87,2:41:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的三万元 -不，所以不成立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-...$30,000 of yours. -No. That's why it wasn't valid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:10.75,2:41:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被敲诈的 你们想知道什么就问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I was being extorted. I'll tell you what you want to know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:14.09,2:41:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不需要隐藏 -最经典的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}PHlLlP: I've got nothing to hide. NICKY: Now for the best.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:16.21,2:41:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信派斯康的花费记录 竟然成了关键\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I couldn't believe this shit. Piscano's expense reports took the cake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:20.72,2:41:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-这太好了 -他干脆就把蓝图给他们算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Oh, this is good. NICKY: He might as well give them a blueprint.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:24.18,2:41:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人的名字、地址、日期 一切都在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Everybody's names, addresses, dates, everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:27.81,2:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是多谢你了，派斯康先生 你真是体帖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Thank you so much, Mr. Piscano. How considerate of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:31.31,2:41:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是我妈的账目 -你被逮捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Those are my mother's books. -You're under arrest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:34.15,2:41:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-真是个蠢才 -你在干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: What a fucking balloon head. ARTIE: What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:36.78,2:41:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷静点 -等一下！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}AGENT: Take it easy. WIFE: Wait!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:39.11,2:41:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-等一下，他有病！ -走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}WIFE: Wait! He's sick! COP: Move back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:41.24,2:41:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-是心脏，还呼吸吗？ -快人工呼吸！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}WIFE: It's his heart! Is he breathing? COP 2: CPR now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:43.70,2:41:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,艾提被搞到心脏病发…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: Artie got so upset he had a heart attack...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:45.83,2:41:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当他老婆的面就挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}and dropped dead right in front of his wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:48.25,2:41:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷静点！ -我无法冷静！\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-Calm down! -No, I won't calm down!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:50.21,2:41:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是我丈夫，艾提！ -我们也不能…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}-He's my husband! Artie! -We can't help him if--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:56.38,2:41:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,最后…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: At the end of the day...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:41:57.84,2:42:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们终于拿照片来给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}they finally came to see me with the pictures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:00.42,2:42:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要保护一个背叛你的朋友？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}FBI AGENT: Why protect a friend who betrayed you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:03.09,2:42:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但我并不想看它们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}SAM: But I didn't want to look at them...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:05.10,2:42:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,或是拿照片来的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}or the guys who brought them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:10.27,2:42:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大人，你可看见，\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}COUNSELOR: Your Honor, as you can see,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:11.51,2:42:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的客户们 都年事已大并生病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}my clients are elderly and infirm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:13.85,2:42:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,任何的刑责都将会 严重威胁到他们的健康\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}COUNSELOR: Any incarceration could pose a serious health risk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:17.11,2:42:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当老大们被逮时 有些简直老到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: When they were arrested, some were so old...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:19.44,2:42:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,罪状认否程序时都需要医师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}they needed doctors at their arraignment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:21.36,2:42:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,预审时建议将保释金额 维持现额\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}COUNSELOR: Pre-trial services recommends that bail remain as set.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:24.53,2:42:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在休庭 -当情况看来他们似乎…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}JUDGE: Take recess. NICKY: When it looked like they'd get...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:27.33,2:42:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,得为了抽头而关上25年时…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}25 years to life in prison just for skimming a casino...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:30.37,2:42:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有病没病 总有人要倒霉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}sick or no fucking sick, you knew people were going to get clipped.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:34.92,2:42:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在罪状认否程序那天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}So the day of the arraignment,{\r}
