Dialogue: 0,2:42:39.34,2:42:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当类似的事发生时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}When something like this happens,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:41.38,2:42:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你已知道事情会怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}you know how things are gonna work out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:43.55,2:42:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是不要有目击者 那安迪呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's always better with no witnesses. So what about Andy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:47.93,2:42:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会说的，史东是好家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He won't talk. Stone is a good kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:51.06,2:42:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他老爸一样带种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Stand-up guy just like his old man.{\r}
