Dialogue: 0,2:42:55.23,2:42:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意，他很强悍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}I agree. He's solid. He's a fucking Marine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:42:59.36,2:43:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他没问题，一直都是 你说呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He's okay. He always was. What do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:05.16,2:43:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要冒险呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Look, why take a chance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:11.29,2:43:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这么想的啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}At least that's the way I feel about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:14.25,2:43:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,打给艾提，告诉他不管怎样…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}ANDY: Call Artie. Tell him I don't care what...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:17.59,2:43:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他星期四都得来我办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}he's gotta be in my office Thursday morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:19.75,2:43:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:20.88,2:43:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,非常重要 我一定得跟他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}It's terribly important. I gotta have a conversation with him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:32.14,2:43:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他们多喜欢他 他还不是家族一员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}NICKY: As much as they liked him, he wasn't one of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:34.94,2:43:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是意大利人 对他们来说，他随时可能供出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He wasn't Italian. As far as they knew, he could have talked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:38.32,2:43:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然他可能还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}Otherwise, he'd still be alive.{\r}
