Dialogue: 0,2:43:45.16,2:43:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个翘头的就是约翰南斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}The first one to skip was John Nance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:43:47.57,2:43:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哥斯大黎加 找了个又好又隐密的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs13\b0\1c&H3CA8DC&}He found a nice, warm, secluded place in Costa Rica.{\r}
